name: BusinessObjects Template
summary: Learn about .RET files and view a list of programs that open them.

content: BusinessObjects templates may be included with the software or may be created by the user. Templates can be saved by selecting "File→Save As→BusinessObjects Templates (*.ret)." They can be loaded by choosing "Select a template" in the New Report Wizard. The default template is named "default.ret."
